  "title": "Human Resource Executive (1 year contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle HR administrative tasks including employee records, onboarding, and offboarding</li><li>Support recruitment activities such as job postings, resume screening, and interview coordination</li><li>Assist in Learning & Development administration, including training coordination and records management</li><li>Maintain HR databases and prepare basic HR reports</li><li>Coordinate employee documentation and ensure records are up to date</li><li>Provide general HR support as required</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree in Human Resources, Business Administration, or related field</li><li>At least 1 year of  HR experience; fresh graduates with relevant internship experiences will be considered</li><li>Strong organizational and administrative skills</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Proficient in MS Office applications</li><li>Retail industry exposure or interest is a strong plus</li></ul><p>If you have what it takes, please send your resume to syafiqah@ambition.com.sg or click APPLY NOW.<br />Data provided is for recruitment purposes only. Regrettably, only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />Business Reg No : 200611680D | Licence No : 10C5117 | EA Reg No : R2199023</p>",
